value.0: This is a baton, used for gongs.

Be warned traveller, the crypts beyond are heavily trapped. The doors are locked, and will lock behind you, and there is a great evil beneath. Not many that set foot into these crypts return, and those that do. You have been warned.
If you listen closely, you can hear the brass gong resonating softly with your every step, as if acknowledging your presence.
